---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>About AgCalculator</title>
    <meta name="description" content="What AgCalculator is, who it's for, and how we keep it fast, accurate, and privacy-friendly." />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://agcalculator.com/about/" />
  </Fragment>

  <header><div class="wrap"><a href="/">← AgCalculator</a></div></header>

  <main class="wrap" style="max-width:760px">
    <h1>About AgCalculator</h1>
    <p>AgCalculator is a collection of lightweight, offline-friendly calculators for farmers, ranchers, and rural landowners. Each tool focuses on a single job and loads fast on slow or spotty connections.</p>

    <h2>What we publish</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Practical calculators (fencing, grain storage, hay bales, and more)</li>
      <li>Plain-language explanations of formulas and assumptions</li>
      <li>Examples so you can sanity-check results in the field</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Accuracy & assumptions</h2>
    <p>Formulas and default values come from common industry practices and manufacturer specs when available. Results are estimates only—always verify measurements and local requirements before purchasing materials or operating equipment.</p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>We don’t collect personal data inside calculators. Basic, privacy-respecting analytics (via Plausible) help us understand which tools are useful. See our <a href="/privacy/">Privacy</a> page for details.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions or suggestions for a new calculator? Email <a href="mailto:info@cleverhayseed.com">info@cleverhayseed.com</a>.</p>

    <p style="color:#64748b"><small>Last updated {new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10)}</small></p>
  </main>

  <style>
    :root{--green:#2F855A;--slate:#334155}
    .wrap{max-width:960px;margin:0 auto;padding:1rem}
    h1{margin:.5rem 0 1rem;color:var(--green)}
    h2{margin:1.25rem 0 .5rem}
    ul{margin:.25rem 0 0 1.2rem}
  </style>
</Layout>
